"Grain, mixed", "Nuts nes",
"Oilcrops", "Oilcrops, Cake Equivalent", "Oilcrops, Oil Equivalent", "Oilseeds nes",
"Pulses nes", "Pulses, Total",
"Roots and Tubers, Total",  "Roots and tubers nes",
"Sugar crops nes", "Spices nes", "Treenuts, Total",
"Vegetables, leguminous nes", "Vegetables Primary", "Vegetables, fresh nes")
